Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time between Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time it takes Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to be performed after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average cycle time of Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in variants that include re-submission loops
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE occurs

Name: Total elapsed time between Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time until Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE occurs in cases that eventually lead to Payment Handled
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time it takes Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to follow Declaration REJECTED by MISSING
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between consecutive occurrences of Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE when preceded by multiple rejection steps
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to the subsequent Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time between Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the next approval activity (e.g., Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average cycle time of Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE compared to the cycle time of Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION in the same variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE across all variants containing at least one rejection loop
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION occurs

Name: Average time it takes Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to occur after the initial Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE in multi-rejection variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Elapsed time between Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and Request Payment in successful end-to-end variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in cases that eventually complete
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time between Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and Payment Handled in variants with a single rejection cycle
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average duration of the entire rejection-handling sub-process starting with any rejection activity and ending with Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time between Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the next occurrence of Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER in relevant variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
